This paper deals with the optimization of wireless power transfer networks, which involves the control and communication between devices. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the design and evaluation of protocols, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper deals with the efficiency and optimization of energy transfer, which could fall under cs.ET (Emerging Technologies). The paper also involves information theory and communication, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper deals with the reduction of carbon footprint, which could fall under cs.PE (Performance Evaluation).
